==English==

===Etymology===
From [[trial]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]
Trialware is a combination of [[freeware]] and [[shareware]]. 

===Noun===
'''trialware'''

#{{cattag|Internet}} Software that allows its use for a limited time period, after which its use  is limited.    


